Ask North: Wales wing George North responds to fans' questions
Sport Wales asked for questions to be posed to Wales and Northampton Saints star George North.The 2013 British and Irish Lions wing tackles questions as varied as whether he would consider playing American Football in the NFL and who is the fastest - the Flash or Superman?Watch Sport Wales on Friday nights on BBC Two Wales. Sport Wales is available on iPlayer for 30 days after transmission.